{
  "name": "RPlog_Ambushing_Jedi",
  "title": "Ambushing Jedi",
  "summary": "On Imperial-occupied Corellia, the Jedi Master Aurejin and his eccentric apprentice Mira are cornered at the Coronet starport when Commander Danik Kreldin, guided by the agent Sinestra (Ms. Starling), surrounds their shuttle Ensorceled with stormtroopers. Aurejin refuses arrest, hurling Danik bodily into the ship with the Force and cutting down boarding troopers with his lightsaber as Mira talks her way free and slips into hiding. With his shuttle rigged with explosives and crippled by E-web fire, Aurejin lifts off in a desperate escape, only for Sinestra to leap aboard the nose for a final knife duel as the Ensorceled detonates over the city and crashes into the Corona House. Danik recovers the Jedi crate Sinestra sought while Mira escapes into the sewers and Aurejin falls free of the blast, locked in mortal struggle with Sinestra. Afterward Sinestra collects her prize and orders the hunt for both Jedi to continue.",
